                The Lord President of the Council (Mr. Herbert Morrison)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-fd567c31-d187-4022-91c3-bd9e9a82ee2d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
